<center><br><a rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i67.tinypic.com/2vlumtg.jpg"></a>
<br>

<br>
<i><h2>"Failure to train IS training to fail" </i>
<br><font color="blue"><a href="https://securitytrainingcenters.com/" rel="nofollow">www.securitytrainingcenters.com</a></font> </h2>
<br>
<br>
Secureone Security Security Training Centers is a leader in providing advanced security officer training to the Chicago area.  We give you the tools you need to be successful in the industry beyond just the requirements of the State.  Please visit our website today for class schedule - below is a special offering for June - join us in a class with another security company we are training.  
<br>
<br>

<h2><font color="blue"><a href="https://securitytrainingcenters.com/class/illinois-concealed-carry-weekend-day-class-031817/" rel="nofollow">Illinois Conceal Carry - 16 hour license course 3/18 - 3/19</a></font></h2>
<h3>This two-day class will will provide training on firearms safety, handling, and laws. Upon completion with a passing score, you will receive a certificate of completion and will be able to apply for your Illinois Concealed Carry License. YOU CANNOT WORK ARMED SECURITY WITH A CCL.  <br></h3><br>



<h2><font color="blue"><a href="https://securitytrainingcenters.com/class/illinois-unarmed-security-20-hour-training-32017-32217/" rel="nofollow">Unarmed Security 20 hour 3/20 - 3/22</a></font></h2>
<h3>This 2.5 day class is for those who want to work in the security field. The 20 hours of training is necessary for employment in contract security in the State of Illinois. <br></h3><br>

<h2><font color="blue"><a href="https://securitytrainingcenters.com/class/illinois-concealed-carry-weekday-day-class-11917-3-2-2-2/" rel="nofollow">Illinois Conceal Carry - 16 hour license course 3/23- 3/24</a></font></h2>
<h3>This two-day class will will provide training on firearms safety, handling, and laws. Upon completion with a passing score, you will receive a certificate of completion and will be able to apply for your Illinois Concealed Carry License. YOU CANNOT WORK ARMED SECURITY WITH A CCL.  <br></h3><br>

<h2><font color="blue"><a href="https://securitytrainingcenters.com/class/crestwood-il-armed-security-officer-20-hour-training-02062017-2-2/&quot;" rel="nofollow">ARMED Security Training 3/22 - 3/24</a></font></h2>
<h3>20 Hour Armed security course required to work as an armed security officer in Illinois.  Upon completion you will receive your qualification in Revolver for security officers. <br></h3><br>

<h2><font color="blue"><a href="https://securitytrainingcenters.com/class/armed-security-range-re-qualification-032517/" rel="nofollow">ARMED Security Range Requalification 03/25/17 9am to Noon</a></font></h2>
<h3>Already ARMED qualified officers looking for their requalification.  We supply the weapon and ammo - you must show proof of training. <br></h3><br>

<h2><font color="blue"><a href="https://securitytrainingcenters.com/class/illinois-security-baton-handcuff-oc-pepper-spray-certification-32817/" rel="nofollow">Baton, Handcuffing, OC-Pepper Spray Certification 3/28/2017</a></font></h2>
<h3>Secureone Training Centers are proud to offer this 1 day course in Baton, Handcuffing and OC - Pepper Spray.  Upon successful completion you will receive certification in each of the 3 core topics.  If you are looking to advance your security career you should always be looking for advanced training.<br></h3><br>

<h2><font color="blue"><a href="https://securitytrainingcenters.com/class/illinois-american-red-cross-first-aidcpraed-certification-class-3217-2/" rel="nofollow">First Aid / CPR / AED - 2 year certification 3/30/17</a></font></h2>
<h3>Would you know what to do in a cardiac, breathing or first-aid emergency? The right answer could help you save a life. With an emphasis on hands-on learning, our First-Aid/CPR/AED course will give you the skills you need to save lives.<br></h3><br>

<h2><font color="blue"><a href="https://securitytrainingcenters.com/classes/" rel="nofollow">Be sure to check out our FULL class schedule</a></font></h2><br><br>
<br>
<br></center>    </section>

